## 6. 電影感運鏡技法 ⭐

| 情緒 | 鏡頭動作 | 參數 |
| --- | --- | --- |
| 平靜 | 緩慢環繞 | angle += 0.15, radius 固定 |
| 緊張 | 推進+微震 | radius 縮小, shake 0.15 |
| 揭示 | 拉遠+俯視 | radius 擴大, height 上升 |
| 高潮 | 動態跟隨 | lookAt 跟隨主體 |
| 結尾 | 緩慢後退 | radius 緩慢擴大 |

**標準運鏡函數:**

```jsx
function updateCamera(time, phase) {
    let targetRadius, targetHeight;
    switch(phase) {
        case 'intro': targetRadius = 22; targetHeight = 5; break;
        case 'conflict': targetRadius = 16; targetHeight = 3; anim.shake = 0.15; break;
        case 'insight': targetRadius = 28; targetHeight = 12; break;
        case 'solution': targetRadius = 18; targetHeight = 6; break;
    }
    anim.camRadius += (targetRadius - anim.camRadius) * 0.025;
    anim.camHeight += (targetHeight - anim.camHeight) * 0.025;
}

```

