## 7. 物體出場動畫庫 ⭐

### 彈性縮放

```jsx
function elasticScale(time, spawnTime, duration = 1) {
    const t = Math.min(1, (time - spawnTime) / duration);
    if (t <= 0) return 0;
    const p = 0.3;
    return Math.pow(2, -10*t) * Math.sin((t-p/4)*(2*Math.PI)/p) + 1;
}

```

### 光爆出現

```jsx
function flashIn(mesh, light, time, spawnTime) {
    const t = time - spawnTime;
    if (t < 0.3) {
        light.intensity = 5 * (1 - t/0.3);
        mesh.material.emissiveIntensity = 2 * (1 - t/0.3);
    }
    mesh.material.opacity = Math.min(1, t / 0.5);
}

```

