## 8. 顏色轉換協議 ⭐

**原則：三位一體**（材質 + 發光 + 光源同步）

```jsx
function transitionColor(mesh, light, targetColor, targetEmissive, intensity, speed = 0.03) {
    mesh.material.color.lerp(new THREE.Color(targetColor), speed);
    mesh.material.emissive.lerp(new THREE.Color(targetEmissive), speed);
    light.color.lerp(new THREE.Color(targetColor), speed);
    light.intensity += (intensity - light.intensity) * speed;
}

```

| 情緒轉換 | 顏色路徑 | Emissive | 光強 |
| --- | --- | --- | --- |
| 平靜→危機 | #00f2ff→#ff0055 | #003344→#330011 | 1→2 |
| 危機→轉機 | #ff0055→#ffcc00 | #330011→#332200 | 2→2.5 |
| 轉機→成就 | #ffcc00→#00f2ff | #332200→#003344 | 2.5→1.5 |

